{"tid":853264,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲打成日覺得自己太好人，成日被人食住上？","createTime":"2018-10-08T12:48:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T14:11:58.000Z","uid":4998,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1fa88c2acf6290acab3d648d4be660c64264a3fe","tid":853264,"uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T12:48:22.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實一路都被人話份人好易相處 好就得人 好識得配合人 係一個典型既和平撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時有啲野明明對某人唔開心我都死忍爛忍<br />\n有時朋友無啦啦發脾四屌晒我老母我都唔會燥返轉頭 <br />\n有時明明唔想食呢樣野 自己唔食既 <br />\n為左朋友開心 我真係無所謂 唔會俾太多意見 我覺得你開心就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n錢銀方面 明明自己都窮撚 有時可能食飯幾餐半餐 你話唔夠錢 我俾多d我都無所謂架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去親旅行都會買手信俾朋友 諗起佢地就會買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  永遠會記得佢地中意乜呢排可能爛左乜 經過一百幾十就順便買俾佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講真 我自問無論朋友又好 以前d ex又好 我真係會好就佢地 對佢地好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但點解我覺得次次都會做左on9仔 有乜都俾人食住上？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來無人會由心去感激你 去了解你可能根本唔中意呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80fb55e7253022a86abf0e37187d52b5f7550553","tid":853264,"uid":185049,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T12:50:08.000Z","msg":"真心 多謝你 仲保持善良不變"},{"pid":"7808489fdf2d70898f938f58f26b2fffc562b3d5","tid":853264,"uid":4998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T12:53:27.000Z","msg":"你地可以屌我唔講無人知你委屈架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實有時我唔介意做付出 做吞聲忍氣個個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只不過我都係人 有啲事 我都會唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我唔講 你夠細心會察覺到<br />\n其實我唔係要一比一既付出 可能我俾一你 你俾返0.1我 我都會好珍惜 我都會記一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n但我覺得自己呢種性格真係好天真<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de4d54014962de75dd51e69c271eb676a00bea8","tid":853264,"uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80fb55e7253022a86abf0e37187d52b5f7550553","tid":853264,"uid":185049,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T12:50:08.000Z","msg":"真心 多謝你 仲保持善良不變"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T12:56:14.000Z","msg":"我想改 我都想下下做食住人個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1792c857868062aee1ada1844f6458160d221a05","tid":853264,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T13:00:19.000Z","msg":"當年係"},{"pid":"714362d98a7393ca2c8ea4f882e3553677c8a200","tid":853264,"uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1792c857868062aee1ada1844f6458160d221a05","tid":853264,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T13:00:19.000Z","msg":"當年係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T13:02:12.000Z","msg":"點改變自己<br />\n我真係覺得自己好on9<br />\n但次次又重覆犯錯<br />\n做好人無光環架<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都唔知為乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea6df5fc95e1c179cf124486ee84b33529fa8e0a","tid":853264,"uid":160099,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T13:02:43.000Z","msg":"我以前都係咁，但依加唔會，對自己好啲啦巴打<br />\n唔係個個都會感激你 呢個世界好現實架<br />\n你係為你自己而活 唔中意咪岀聲<br />\n你啲fd都係顧住自己啦 有理過你咩<br />\n有就唔會食住你啦係咪先"},{"pid":"2a017a2e6a36112a06efb4e0cb7c1a6bdd790229","tid":853264,"uid":185049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8de4d54014962de75dd51e69c271eb676a00bea8","tid":853264,"uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80fb55e7253022a86abf0e37187d52b5f7550553","tid":853264,"uid":185049,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T12:50:08.000